libcio (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release.
  * Polymorphic character I/O with CIOArray, CIOFILE, and CIOUTF8 backends.
  * Circular buffer for efficient buffered reads.
  * UTF-8 codec layer over byte streams.

